                     <interp inst="t18290910-31-person382" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I took the prisoner, and produce the property.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. On coming down the Strand I saw the umbrella leaning towards the ground - there was a great crowd going along, and several people stumbled to pick it up; I took it, and went to have a pint of beer.</p>
